name: Lieutenant Williams
Lore: 'Pilot of the Radiant VII. Was personally requested by Captain Madakor to assist in the transportation of the Jedi ambassadors.',
Text: 'Adds 2 to power of anything he pilots. While piloting Radiant VII and you have no other starships at same system, unless opponent has total ability > 6 piloting here, opponent''s total battle destiny here is -3.',
